# API Routes Guide

This project uses Next.js API routes to handle server-side operations.

## GitHub API
- [src/app/api/github/route.ts](mdc:src/app/api/github/route.ts) - Handles GitHub API interactions

## Service Integration
The API routes work in conjunction with:
- [src/services/github.ts](mdc:src/services/github.ts) - Client-side service that calls these API routes
- [src/hooks/useGitHubProjects.ts](mdc:src/hooks/useGitHubProjects.ts) - Hook that utilizes the GitHub service
